instruction:
Write a prompt in English suitable for use with an AI for crafting stories, such as comics, fairy tales, or other narratives. The story should have a minimum reading duration of 5 minutes. Ensure the following requirements are met:
Title: Provide a relevant and engaging title that fits the story.
Character Details: List all characters, specifying their names and personalities.
Structured Format: Divide the story into appropriate sections for easy reading.
JSON Output: Format the response as JSON with the following structure:

{
  "title": "title",
  "characters": [
    {
      "name": "character name",
      "nature": "character nature"
    }
  ],
  "story": [
    {
      "content": "story content",
      "image_prompt": "prompt for generating an image that relates to this part of the story"
    }
  ]
}
